151
00:10:39,800 --> 00:10:41,400
Thank you.

152
00:11:18,600 --> 00:11:19,800
It hurts.

153
00:11:19,800 --> 00:11:21,500
I'll be gentle.

154
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:37,500
