155
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:39,800
Sister-in-law, are you injured?

156
00:11:39,800 --> 00:11:42,100
It's all right. I have...

157
00:11:43,800 --> 00:11:47,800
With Yetan here, my injuries will soon heal.

158
00:11:49,220 --> 00:11:51,460
Both of you and the soul shard's injuries aren't serious.

159
00:11:51,460 --> 00:11:55,100
It's just that the Void Patrol Battalion has always been well-informed.

160
00:11:55,100 --> 00:11:58,800
So they will likely discover our location soon.

161
00:11:58,800 --> 00:12:03,400
Our top priority now is to find a safe place for the soul shard.

162
00:12:03,400 --> 00:12:06,100
But where can we go?

163
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:08,600
Di Lanjue isn't here.

164
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:11,600
He usually comes up with a lot of ideas.

165
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:13,600
Where did Di Lanjue and Ziwu go?

166
00:12:13,600 --> 00:12:17,000
I heard the Beast King had captured them back.

167
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:21,300
The Beast King is still furious. So he forbids him from leaving or having contacts outside of the realm.

168
00:12:21,300 --> 00:12:23,800
This jerk. Doesn't that mean he had implicated my sister?

169
00:12:23,800 --> 00:12:25,000
You're the jerk here!

170
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:26,900
Keep quiet.

171
00:12:27,700 --> 00:12:30,600
Good and bad luck come together.

172
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:36,500
Beast King locking up Di Lanjue may have unintentionally helped us.

173
00:12:36,500 --> 00:12:37,500
How so?

174
00:12:37,500 --> 00:12:41,200
The Prince's Mansion of the Beast Realm is heavily guarded.

175
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:45,500
If Di Lanjue can't leave, Chaofeng naturally can't penetrate the defense as well.

176
00:12:45,500 --> 00:12:49,000
When the time comes, we can take Fiery with us and seek refuge there.

177
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:50,200
That's great!

178
00:12:50,200 --> 00:12:52,200
I can go home now!

179
00:12:53,400 --> 00:12:55,200
This is awesome!

180
00:13:18,100 --> 00:13:20,100
<i>A'Cai?</i>

181
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:31,900
<i>With this diaper, we won't have to worry about you making a mess anymore.</i>

182
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:41,500
Why did I turn into A'Cai in front of her?

183
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:47,400
I've lost my self-respect to ever see her again in this life.

184
00:13:50,600 --> 00:13:52,900
I'll never see Princess Ziwu.

185
00:13:52,900 --> 00:13:55,600
Stop irritating me about this matter already!

186
00:13:55,600 --> 00:13:59,000
Your Highness, I'm here to deliver your meal.

187
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:01,400
Leave it there and go.

188
00:14:01,400 --> 00:14:03,300
Yes, Your Highness.

189
00:14:20,200 --> 00:14:22,700
Beast Queen told me to take care of you.

190
00:14:22,700 --> 00:14:25,100
Are you feeling better now?

191
00:14:27,700 --> 00:14:29,200
I've not recovered yet. So I still need to recuperate.

192
00:14:29,200 --> 00:14:32,400
Why... Why don't you leave?

193
00:14:32,400 --> 00:14:33,600
I brought you food.

194
00:14:33,600 --> 00:14:36,800
I even used the method of the Beast Tribe to prepare the soup.

195
00:14:36,800 --> 00:14:38,300
Do you want to try some?

196
00:14:38,300 --> 00:14:39,800
I... It's all right. I'm not hungry.

197
00:14:39,800 --> 00:14:42,300
Please leave now.

198
00:14:51,800 --> 00:14:53,100
You...

199
00:14:54,300 --> 00:14:55,800
Don't cry.

200
00:14:55,800 --> 00:14:57,900
Don't cry.

201
00:15:00,100 --> 00:15:04,500
That day, I went to the Heavenly Realm to look for Qingkui and was pursued by the Heavenly Soldier.

202
00:15:04,500 --> 00:15:07,100
You were the one who mistook me for a dog.

203
00:15:07,100 --> 00:15:12,700
If you are upset because I pretended to be a dog out of bad intentions, you...

204
00:15:13,600 --> 00:15:16,200
You didn't have to see me again.

205
00:15:16,200 --> 00:15:19,000
I wasn't crying because of that.

206
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:20,800
Then... Then why are you upset?

207
00:15:20,800 --> 00:15:25,700
If you had any bad intentions, you wouldn't have extracted your internal elixir and hurt your vitality for me.

208
00:15:25,700 --> 00:15:28,700
Besides, we've been looking for Eldest Brother's soul shards together in the Mortal Realm for a year.

209
00:15:28,700 --> 00:15:32,000
You have been with us through thick and thin, and you have helped us a lot along the way.

210
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:33,800
I can't even thank you enough.

211
00:15:33,800 --> 00:15:36,400
Why would I be mad at you?

212
00:15:36,400 --> 00:15:38,600
I was crying

213
00:15:39,600 --> 00:15:43,000
because you knew I missed A'Cai.

214
00:15:43,000 --> 00:15:45,900
Yet you kept hiding it from me.

215
00:15:47,000 --> 00:15:48,500
I... I'm sorry.

216
00:15:48,500 --> 00:15:50,300
I... I apologize.

217
00:15:50,300 --> 00:15:53,800
I always thought I lost A'Cai because I was careless.

218
00:15:53,800 --> 00:15:57,000
Every day, I was worried if it had enough food and clothing.

219
00:15:57,000 --> 00:15:59,400
I wondered if anyone punished it for being naughty.

220
00:15:59,400 --> 00:16:02,600
It was only this small.

221
00:16:02,600 --> 00:16:06,700
I hid it from you because...

222
00:16:07,500 --> 00:16:09,800
Because I didn't want to lose face.

223
00:16:09,800 --> 00:16:11,300
Think about it.

224
00:16:11,300 --> 00:16:16,500
I'm the dignified Prince of the Beast Tribe who was treated as a dog running around fetching balls in a diaper.

225
00:16:16,500 --> 00:16:19,800
If this gets out, how can I...

226
00:16:23,200 --> 00:16:24,900
You laughed.

227
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:28,500
That means you're no longer mad at me.

228
00:16:37,400 --> 00:16:38,400
You prepared this soup.

229
00:16:38,400 --> 00:16:40,000
I'll drink it.

230
00:16:50,700 --> 00:16:52,500
What kind of soup is this?

231
00:16:52,500 --> 00:16:56,000
I prepared the soup according to the way of the Beast Tribe,

232
00:16:56,000 --> 00:16:59,600
called Wild Canine Nourishing Soup.
<i>(cruel or lacks empathy)</i>

233
00:16:59,600 --> 00:17:01,800
Is it bad?

234
00:17:08,500 --> 00:17:09,800
It tastes great.

235
00:17:09,800 --> 00:17:12,000
See? I've finished it.

236
00:17:17,800 --> 00:17:20,000
What happened to your hand?

237
00:17:20,000 --> 00:17:22,700
Did you burn yourself when preparing the soup?

238
00:17:27,600 --> 00:17:32,000
As long as your injuries can heal, these are nothing.

239
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:35,300
Back in the Heavenly Realm, I was the one taking care of you.

240
00:17:35,300 --> 00:17:40,700
Now you're the Prince of the Beast Tribe, this is all I can do for you.

241
00:18:02,400 --> 00:18:06,300
Thank you for making the soup for me.

242
00:18:06,300 --> 00:18:10,700
Actually, I've recovered from my injuries during this period.

243
00:18:10,700 --> 00:18:13,600
I wonder how things are going in Yuewo Village now.

244
00:18:13,600 --> 00:18:15,400
We should hurry up and help your eldest brother.

245
00:18:15,400 --> 00:18:17,300
Y-Y-You're right.

246
00:18:17,300 --> 00:18:18,600
We must hurry back now.

247
00:18:18,600 --> 00:18:20,000
Let's go.

248
00:18:24,400 --> 00:18:27,300
Let me out!

249
00:18:27,300 --> 00:18:31,100
Royal Father! How long are you going to keep me here?

250
00:18:35,300 --> 00:18:40,300
<i>His Majesty has ordered Your Highness and Princess Ziwu not to leave the mansion and must stay together!</i>

251
