Heartless Shaodian's second soul shard.

510
00:35:50,140 --> 00:35:51,560
I need to wash my clothes again.

511
00:35:51,560 --> 00:35:53,193
Yes.

512
00:35:59,000 --> 00:36:01,100
Sorry to keep you waiting.

513
00:36:01,100 --> 00:36:02,140
